Clean up workbench initialization and use CDN for webview in production

Makes the workbench initialization async, reads configuration from URL
parameters (origin, function, vsCodeCdn, isDevo), falls back to fetching
product.json when no DOM config element exists, and sets the webview
endpoint to the CDN origin in non-devo environments.

